ISLAMABAD, Jun 21 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi Monday expressed his grief over the sad demise of former senator and leader of Pakhtunkhwa Milli Awami Party Usman Kakar.
He, in a message, prayed for the departed soul and conveyed his condolences to the bereaved family.
